- **Tier 3**: 99% (Standard)
- **Tier 4**: 99.5% (Microservices)

**Error Budget Policy**:
- Green (>50%): Normal development
- Yellow (20-50%): Focus reliability
- Red (<20%): Feature freeze
- Critical (0%): Emergency response

