- Network (throughput, errors)
- Load average

**Container Metrics**: ~20 unique metrics
- CPU usage per container
- Memory usage per container
- Network I/O
- Filesystem usage

**Database Metrics**: ~25 unique metrics
- Connections, queries
- Cache hit ratio
- Locks, deadlocks
- Replication lag
- Transaction rates

**Total**: **~115 unique metrics**, **~10,000 active time series**

